name: "L'IMPERATRICE"
description:
L'IMPERATRICE :I touch it, I taste it, I eat it and again ... my energy is explosive, and you can only be dazzled, blinded by it.
waste is my risk. like a rumble, without realizing it, the teenage years have passed, but not mine, an eternal blossoming.

This card is part of an original tarot deck made by Rahtattoo. 
The 22 works that compose it are the result of the study of the ancient symbolism that animates the tarot's major arcana.
